# ZeroGate — Code Owners
# Security-sensitive paths require explicit review before merge.

# Default: all changes require review
*                               @your-org/platform-team

# Infrastructure changes — require infrastructure + security review
/infrastructure/                @your-org/platform-team @your-org/security-team

# Auth flow + access policies — require security team review
/docker/authentik/              @your-org/security-team
/docker/cloudflared/            @your-org/security-team
/policies/                      @your-org/security-team

# CI pipeline — require platform team review
/.github/                       @your-org/platform-team
